products.name: ABS Master gaming PC (ALI489)
products.description:
A power-packed PC that takes on everyday computing with speed and ease, from browsing and streaming to gaming. A 10th generation Intel Core i5-10400F processor (6 cores, 12 threads) pairs with a GeForce RTX 3060 GPU-based graphics card to take on the latest AAA titles in a breeze. A clean-designed mid tower case has tempered glass front and side panels to showcase your build bathed in RGB lighting. Gaming-grade keyboard and mouse are bundled for straight play out of the box. 
Intel Core i5 10th Gen 10400F (2.90GHz)
GeForce RTX 3060 12GB
16GB DDR4 3000MHz
512GB SSD
Windows 10 Home 64-bit
Gaming Keyboard & Mouse
VR Ready

products.name: Seagate STEL10000400 10TB
products.description:
Two integrated high-speed USB 3.0 ports on the front allow you to connect and recharge your other USB devices.
    Windows and Mac compatible. Install the provided NTFS driver for Mac as needed, and you can use the Backup Plus Hub interchangeably between Windows and Mac computers without reformatting.
    With the Seagate Dashboard software, you can smartly manage your backups. Run a one-click backup or schedule an automatic backup plan to protect your files.
    Install the free Seagate Mobile Backup app on an iOS or Android mobile device, and back up all of the photos and videos from your device to your Seagate drive or to the cloud.
